Body covered: Quick Reference, 6 detailed steps (branch confirmation, avoid cherry-pick of submodule pointers, detect justfile recipe collisions, rebase, force-with-lease, wait for GitHub re-evaluation), 5 Failed Attempts, Results & Parameters (submodule pin facts, Harden checks CI scope, justfile conflict resolution, rename collision pattern), Verified On Odysseus 2026-05-04.
